prompt_text: Describe the smartphone application that you use the most.
content_text: Smartphone application that I use the most is WhatsApp. Through WhatsApp, I can get it. I can stay in touch with my friends, I can discuss whatever I want to. I can talk to them. There there are so many facilities. There are so many features of WhatsApp. I can make them video calls, I can send them audio messages, I can send them photographs, videos. And many more things. WhatsApp is. Very good at times. In case if the phone is, if your phone is not working. You can call. Your friends.
